<HEADLINE> HKSAR Provisional Regional Council Holds 1st Meeting </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, July 4 (Xinhua) -- The Provisional Regional Council
of the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region (HKSAR) held its
first meeting here this afternoon.
</P>
<P>
