legislative authorities is to pay back salaries to the military,
teachers and doctors," Yeltsin continued.
</P>
<P>
Speaking of the domestic industrial output, the president said
the prime cost of industrial output will diminish following a cut
in the rate of interest on credits, in tariffs on transport, gas
and electric power and a reduction in taxes this year. 
