the Congolese force was stricken between Ugandan President Y.
Museveni and President Kabila of Democratic Congo at his swearing
in ceremony in May in Kinshasa.
</P>
<P>
Uganda is gaining a reputation of being the best police
trainers in the region. Last year, Ugandan police officers went
to Rwanda to rub their skill on the then untrained new Rwandan
police. 
