<HEADLINE> Venezuelan Exports Up in Early 1997 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CARACAS, July 3 (Xinhua) -- Venezuelan non-traditional exports
reached 1.83 billion U.S. dollars in the first five months of the
year, a 14.3 percent increase over the same period last year, the
press reported today.
