<HEADLINE> Sestriere Athletics Meeting Cancelled </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ROME, July 3 (Xinhua) -- The Grand Prix athletics meeting
scheduled here for July 19 has been cancelled due to financial and
management difficulties, organizers said on Thursday.
</P>
<P>
The northern Italian resort staged the Alpine Skiing World
Championships in February and officials from the Sestriere sports
club said it was impossible to host another international event so
soon afterwards.
</P>
<P>
The Sestriere athletics meeting has gained a reputation for
producing impressive performances in the recent years. 
</P>
</TEXT>
